3 December 2008Government Spokesperson, Themba Maseko, will brief media on the outcomes of the Cabinet meeting held yesterday, 3 December 2008. He will be joined by Ms Lindiwe Hendricks, Minister of Water Affairs and Forestry, who will discuss the country s water and its safety.Details are as follows: Date: 4 December 2008 Time: 10:00 Venue: Room 153, Union Buildings, PretoriaNote: There will be a video link to the Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town.Enquiries Bongiwe Gambu (Pretoria) Cell: 082 714 9463Colin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)